ji\" /> ，只要加上酸甜醬掩飾，冷凍的冰箱味，還是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發餿味都可以瞞天過海，而且還能引發食慾，所以如果你告訴我新鮮的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要做酸甜口味，我會大叫真是暴殄天物啊！"},{"pid":"c0a0fbc80859b576bd500d3680f4ddf9115b496e","tid":845803,"uid":181432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ea1fc45abaf9aef4cea5ce834cddfd373f9d2255","tid":845803,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:01:06.000Z","msg":"早兩日放假，上咗男友屋企，之後我地開咗支86紅酒飲，飲到咁上下大家都慶慶地，佢問我準備好未，我話ok吖。。<br />\n一開始嗰陣都冇乜嘢嘅，但係我男友一伸個頭落去，奶都未開始奶就灑手兼擰頭，話咩：一陣死海鮮味<br />\n之後佢就去咗沖涼瞓教，冇再理我，各位絲打，我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 150 80kg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/112944_7ebec91a5b0eb2a5a0946f749409749f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F112944_7ebec91a5b0eb2a5a0946f749409749f.gif&h=2d135aa0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ba9fb466081b2fd8cf9cef1a126a27403813145","tid":845803,"uid":209092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:32:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0477d38193dac607cb7ad4436c0b634ecf21e73e","tid":845803,"uid":41992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ba9fb466081b2fd8cf9cef1a126a27403813145","tid":845803,"uid":209092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bbb57882f1f90327f1e9561d9869be7d2483402","tid":845803,"uid":41992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b0d84fdaa0e1efa170e2c863340a8e5328ec2150","tid":845803,"uid":120355,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/111349_655132225d290ea79b4a69962f816f28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2